{"id":264119,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-山东莱州上访维权者王伟平夫妇被关黑监/","date":"2012-11-20T18:15:51Z","modified":"2012-11-20T18:15:51Z","title":"维权网 | 山东莱州上访维权者王伟平夫妇被关黑监狱13天后获释","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）本网信息员获悉：山东省莱州市平里店镇柳行村上访维权者王伟平、郝伟英夫妇被关黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>天后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点</span><span>，分别从各自被关的黑监狱中获释回到家中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，王伟平、郝伟英夫妇于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span>，在北京朝阳区被当地平里店镇政府工作人员截获，当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点夫妇俩被押回莱州。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王伟平被镇政府人员关押在好家商务所酒楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>楼的一间房子，一直到获释前都有人严密看守。而郝伟英先被弄进公安局拘留所关押，由于在关押期间郝伟英一直不停反抗，并要求警方开具拘留通知书给她，遭到公安局无理拒绝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点，镇政府工作人员将郝伟英从拘留所转到莱州市雅惠宾馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>号房关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>等到中共十八会议闭幕，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点</span><span>，王伟平、郝伟英夫妇被关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>天之后，结束了被非法关押的生活。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王伟平手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15953545309</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7133157365368229903?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa